# The libFuzzer corpus and crash reproducers are NOT committed to git. The corpus is
# persisted across CI runs via GitHub Actions cache (key `fuzz-corpus-*`), grown by the
# scheduled fuzz campaign and restored (read-only) by the PR corpus-replay gate — see
# .github/workflows/workflow_gen/src/workflow_gen/workflows/fuzz.py. Crash reproducers are
# uploaded as the `fuzz-artifacts` workflow artifact on failure, not tracked here.
corpus/
artifacts/
target/
